{"tid":1585362,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"上海 5G 巡邏機械人投入應用  360 度無死角監控","createTime":"2019-09-21T14:38:31.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-27T10:59:01.000Z","uid":325424,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"19631c1f6c0e1b88a031be3203f9fbf7ab371bf4","tid":1585362,"uid":325424,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-21T14:38:31.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://unwire.hk/2019/09/17/china-5g-robot-surveillance/fun-tech/?fbclid=IwAR1A8PyLsbgQXFV5mrXmDGcGFn8QHs-FE_9hW-kWMSLA_OQXjYqYMDyaFco\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Funwire.hk%2F2019%2F09%2F17%2Fchina-5g-robot-surveillance%2Ffun-tech%2F%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR1A8PyLsbgQXFV5mrXmDGcGFn8QHs-FE_9hW-kWMSLA_OQXjYqYMDyaFco&d=zoPJ6Qh4RBVN8MuZ9mClYvrgBFspSC5jYnxvlVik22g%3D&h=d31cfd79\" target=\"_blank\">https://unwire.hk/2019/09/17/china-5g-robot-surveillance/fun-tech/?fbclid=IwAR1A8PyLsbgQXFV5mrXmDGcGFn8QHs-FE_9hW-kWMSLA_OQXjYqYMDyaFco</a><br />\n中國監控技術超英趕美，最近在 5G 技術開始普及之際，亦終於推出了 5G 巡邏機械人，結合多個鏡頭和感應器，加上人臉辨識等功能，可以 24 小時運作。首批機械人已經開始在上海投入測試。<br />\n<br />\n在上海南京東路開始投入測試的巡邏機械人搭載四個廣角高清鏡頭、一個紅外熱成像鏡頭和一個變焦高清鏡頭，其升降式雲台更可以全角度旋轉，最高可升至 1.8 米，實時監控街上的人潮和路面情況，系統亦連接到中央系統，可以即時傳送實時影像以及進行人臉辨識。機械人也內置中英文語音，可以根據不同情況播放宣傳內容。<br />\n<br />\n南京東路派出所民警表示：「它自動巡邏的功能，彌補人工上的不足，可實現24小時在戶外進行巡邏；在人流量大的地鐵口和步行街，可設置語音播報等安全提示；未來經過升級調試以及5G技術的應用，可實現市民通過攝像頭和後台民警即時對話。」目前機械人只在南京東路投入應用，未來相信會逐步擴充應用範圍。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2019/09/70451790_2396904990551172_8772232245495726080_o.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.unwire.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F09%2F70451790_2396904990551172_8772232245495726080_o.jpg&h=ed5e1a06&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"96f838e4a9ef2e9b739071399fa86fb29db59e31","tid":1585362,"uid":325424,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-21T14:41:07.000Z","msg":"[人面識別] 你以為剩係電燈柱先有？黨企中國海外/中國建築地盤會裝人面識別系統<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1576481\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1576481</a>"},{"pid":"d3cf8a79bccc159aa3b4c204eff0b726a57179d4","tid":1585362,"uid":325424,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T23:31:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ff841da996fd4a6f5e941aa0c7178b3c93dc598e","tid":1585362,"uid":53705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T15:05:32.000Z","msg":"部機械人有冇武器?? 例如機槍??<br />\n<br />\n如果無既話, 成班路人夾手夾腳 拆左佢都得啦"},{"pid":"7b626f5628ed9f312be37403ec07422cdf4a8016","tid":1585362,"uid":325424,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ff841da996fd4a6f5e941aa0c7178b3c93dc598e","tid":1585362,"uid":53705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T15:05:32.000Z","msg":"部機械人有冇武器?? 例如機槍??<br />\n<br />\n如果無既話, 成班路人夾手夾腳 拆左佢都得啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T10:59:01.000Z","msg":"拆佢唔知有咩後果"}]}